	<!-- TEXT  -->
	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SOLOMONS_MINES_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>All That Glitters</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SOLOMONS_MINES_HELP">
			<Text>*The messanger is out of breath, clearly his news is urgent*[NEWLINE]Your Excellency... I bear a message direct from The Mines... A new chamber has been opened... You are summoned.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SOLOMONS_MINES_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>The Natural Wonder permenantly yields +1 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production, [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism and [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SOLOMONS_MINES_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>A couple of Barbarian Units spawn near the City. In response, the citizen supply a Free Armoury which generates +2 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SOLOMONS_MINES_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Pay {2_InstantYield} to construct a Well which provides a copy of [ICON_RES_GEMS] Gems.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SOLOMONS_MINES_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Pay {2_InstantYield} to construct a Watermill which provides a copy of [ICON_RES_GOLD] Gold.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SOLOMONS_MINES_HELP_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>Allow the excavation, costing -5 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production per turn. The local Museum receives +5 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science and +5 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SOLOMONS_MINES_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>*The miners have discovered yet more tunnels filled with metal*[NEWLINE]Excellent, the wealth of the Earth is apparently inexhaustible.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SOLOMONS_MINES_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>*Reaching a cavern lit by a topless chimney and filled with filled with tropical flora, the miners have stumbled upon a forgotten civilization of near-sightless savages*[NEWLINE]On the surface, these bizzare troglodytes will be no match for are well-armed militia. But fight these things in their home? It is a suicide mission. The locals will have to be ever vigilant of future incursions.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SOLOMONS_MINES_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>*We have broken through to an enormous underground reservoir, lined with gemstones!*[NEWLINE]Send our mechanics immediately! A huge Well to dredge up Gemstones, how fantastical!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SOLOMONS_MINES_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>*We have broken through to a raging underground river, fleked with gold dust!*[NEWLINE]Send our mechanics immediately! An underground Watermill to sift Gold, Good Heavens!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SOLOMONS_MINES_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>*The walls of the newest levels are littered with petrified creatures!*[NEWLINE]The wonders of The Mines are ceaseless! Send a team of excavators to dig up these fossils and have them sent to the Museum for analysis!</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
